---

<div class="container my-8 md:my-16">
  <section
    class="w-full rounded-xl border border-border bg-card px-4 py-8 md:px-8 md:py-12 shadow-sm"
  >

  <div class="flex h-full flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">

    <picture>
      <source srcset="/images/akash-3d.webp" type="image/webp" />
      <img
        src="/images/akash-3d.png"
        alt="Akash"
        width="100"
        height="88"
        class="select-none pointer-events-none"
      />
    </picture>

    <div class="my-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 px-2 md:my-8 md:gap-6 md:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
        The Economic Layer <br class="hidden md:block" /> of the Open Cloud
      </h2>

      <p class="mx-auto max-w-xl text-center text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed text-para md:text-base">
        Powered by the native AKT utility token, our automated settlement layer manages transaction logic in the background. Your teams deploy via standard credit card billing while securing raw market rates.
      </p>
    </div>

    <a
      href="/token/"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-md border border-border bg-transparent px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-foreground transition-colors hover:bg-accent"
    >
      Learn more about AKT
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/></svg>
    </a>

  </div>
  </section>
</div>
